title: Adrian Newey, Racing God, Will Lead The Flock At COTA - /SHAKEDOWN
description:
The US GP F1 race is coming to Circuit of the Americas and Red Bull Racing has championships to win -- Driver via Vettel and Constructors thanks to Adrian Newey.  Leo Parente and ShakeDown discuss what needs to be done to get the job done.  And how Adrian Newey has done so all his career.
